This paper is primarily focused on the security and usability aspects of password composition policies, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). However, the paper also discusses the computational and sample complexity of the problem, which could be relevant to the categories of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), computational complexity (cs.CC), information theory (cs.IT), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
